welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Bothell East, a charming city known for its picturesque surroundings and friendly community. We invite you to explore and immerse yourself in all that this lovely town has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Snohomish County - Paine Field Airport handles all commercial flights and provides a variety of amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: The general aviation terminal at Snohomish County - Paine Field Airport caters to private and charter flights, offering a comfortable and efficient experience for passengers.

wifi.note: Free wifi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Seaplane Terminal
